      "content": "yeah, it's just... it feels like i'm living in a world that doesn't exist anymore. everything is just grey. sometimes i just sit there for hours staring at his chair. i feel like i'm just waiting for something that isn't coming back. it's exhausting to pretend that things will get better.",
